Chain_Info1_Description="Nervos Godwoken is the Layer 2 of Nervos and its solution to support the EVM ecosystem. This EVM-compatible Optimistic Roll-up was designed to enable quick and easy dApp development. The Nervos Layer 1 is a public blockchain that provides the security and decentralization for the Nervos platform, while generating trust and extending to multiple blockchain layers promoting flexibility and scalability. Godwoken is, by nature, a multi-chain solution that leverages advanced account abstraction enabling flexible wallet support and traditional user experience similar to Web 2.<br><br>Similar to the relationship between ETH and Etherreum, CKB, the token used on Nervos Godwoken, is used in executing your smart contracts or for use in dApps and even in renting out space on the blockchain. It can also be used as a medium of exchange and as a store of value."
